OL,3,CAmbulance workers resign after court
OL,4,Cruling over man's death
OL,6,FTwo Jersey ambulance workers convicted
OL,7,Fof failing to provide reasonable care
OL,8,Fto a patient who later died have now
OL,9,Fresigned from the service, ITV News
OL,10,Funderstands.
OL,12,FJohn Sutherland and Tom Le Sauteur
OL,13,Fwere found to have unreasonably
OL,14,Fdelayed treatment of 39-year-old
OL,15,FFrazer Irvine who suffered a cardiac
OL,16,Farrest after a drug overdose.
OL,18,FThe Royal Court heard how the
OL,19,Fambulance workers had called the
OL,20,Fpolice for help as Mr Irvine was
OL,21,Fallegedly being aggressive.
