OL,3,CAmbulance workers resign after court
OL,4,Cruling over man's death
OL,6,FTheir subsequent appeal of the
OL,7,Fconviction failed and Le Sauteur tells
OL,8,FITV News that leaving the ambulance
OL,9,Fservice is a "mutual decision" as he
OL,10,Fnow wants to "finally draw a line"
OL,11,Funder it and move on with his life.
OL,13,FIn a joint response, officials say:
OL,14,F"The Government of Jersey, the
OL,15,FAmbulance Service staff and Unite the
OL,16,FUnion wish John and Tom all the very
OL,17,Fbest in their future endeavours,
OL,18,Frecognising and supporting their
OL,19,Fdecision not to return to the service.
