OL,4,Cruling over man's death
OL,6,FFellow emergency workers described
OL,7,Ftheir situation as a "gross case of
OL,8,Finjustice" as hundreds of people
OL,9,Fdemonstrated outside the ambulance
OL,10,Fheadquarters in St Helier.
OL,12,FDr Kirstie Ross, who works at the
OL,13,FGeneral Hospital, said at the time:
OL,14,F"Any medic knows that the first thing
OL,15,Fwe are taught is, 'Is it safe for us
OL,16,Fto approach?' and it wasn't. We need
OL,17,Fto make sure it is because we're no
OL,18,Fuse to anyone if we get hurt
OL,19,Fourselves."
