OL,6,FHowever, Mr Irvine's family believe
OL,7,Fthat "the actions of the paramedics
OL,8,Ffell well below any acceptable
OL,9,Fstandards of care" and say "efforts to
OL,10,Fportray Frazer as a violent,
OL,11,Faggressive drunk could not be further
OL,12,Ffrom the truth".
